    stretched={true}
    type="error"

    data={{
        "header": ["band", "singer", "rhythm guitar", "lead guitar", "bass", "drums", "keyboard"],

properties.description: Adds padding between series in the chart. 0 means no padding. 0.005 provides 1px relief.

properties.description: Shows labels one the chart. Set up labels in the data object. Example: {"theta": 1, "label": "Apples"}
properties.name: showLabels

properties.description: Specifies the distance between edge of the chart and labels. 1 places labels on the edge of the chart.
properties.name: labelsRadiusMultiplier

properties.description: Styles object that let's you style labels on the chart
properties.name: labelsStyle

properties.description: Specifies the radius of the chart. Value that equals 50% of the height of the entire component equals 100% of the size. Required to create donut chart.
properties.name: radius

properties.name: innerRadius

properties.description: Shows hint on click into every part of the pie chart
properties.name: hint
